  "plan": "1. Check service status with service command. 2. Start mailman3 if not running. 3. Check existing lists. 4. Create the reading-group list with appropriate settings (subscription policy open). 5. Configure postfix to relay to mailman via LMTP. 6. Update /etc/aliases with mailman aliases. 7. Test with eval script. Let's start by checking services and mailman's bin.",
